						<p>Saṅkama—(Date lost).</p>						

						<p>In this badly damaged and mutilated record, only the <hi rend="italic">praśasti</hi> of the king is preserved. The extant date portion is Kārtika, Pūrṇimā. The king is stated to have been ruling from <hi rend="bold">Kalyāṇa.</hi></p>						

